The paper also presents a data analysis platform, which involves manipulating datasets (cs.DB) and using probabilistic inference techniques (cs.LG). The platform uses simple operators, which suggests a focus on algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses measurements and sensitivity, which are topics in information theory (cs.IT).
